title: The Westin Turtle Bay Resort & Spa, Mauritius
description: Contemporary rooms in a luxe resort offering multiple restaurants, beach access & 2 outdoor pools.
hotelDescription:
Facing the Turtle Bay marine park, this luxury resort is 10 km from the Mauritius National Botanical Garden and 13 km from the capital city Port Louis.
 Featuring ocean-view balconies, the modern rooms display flat-screen TVs, iPod docks and free Wi-Fi, as well as minibars, and tea and coffeemakers. Upgraded rooms include access to a lounge providing complimentary breakfast and soft drinks. Some suites have outdoor showers.
 A breakfast buffet (surcharge) is served in a relaxed restaurant. There are also Indian and fusion dining options. Other amenities consist of beach access, 2 outdoor pools and a spa. Golf and water sports can be arranged.

title: InterContinental Resort Mauritius, an IHG Hotel
description: Luxury resort featuring sleek rooms & suites, plus dining, an infinity pool & a spa.
address: Fort Coastal Road, MU, Balaclava 21306, Mauritius
hotelDescription:
Set on the Bay of Balaclava, this posh resort is 10 km from Sir Seewoosagur Ramgoolam Botanical Garden, 13 km from Jummah Masjid historic mosque and 15 km from stamp collections at Blue Penny Museum.
 Sleek rooms offer flat-screen TVs, free Wi-Fi and minibars, as well as bay views. Suites add hot tubs, and terraces or balconies.
 Amenities include upscale dining, a polished beach bar and an outdoor infinity pool, plus tennis courts and a spa.
